{"id": "1427695589855858839", "channel_id": "1427695589855858839", "type": 0, "author_id": "173143524324147200", "author_name": "bumcchi", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hi, I could only find some posts here about this which seems to have been answered via DMs so I'm asking here ´ - `\n\nWhat is the Morimens teams views on fan created Morimens merch? \nI'm aware some companies are okay with fan merch while some are not, as it varies from company to company, so I thought I'd ask here (；´∀｀)", "timestamp": "2025-10-14T16:32:33.923000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1427695589855858839", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Question about fanart & merch", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
{"id": "1427578233032937576", "channel_id": "1427578233032937576", "type": 0, "author_id": "340713722345553921", "author_name": "melwyn7591", "author_bot": false, "content": "During my run in wave 5 dtide, i noticed that ogier's  unstable barrier works differently from what the description said. Rather than tracking the amount of arithmetic used, it resolves to tracking the original arithmetic cost of that card (somehow thais exalt duping card doesnt get affected)\n\nP/S: Also i think that his unstable barrier is a bit unfair with gaining shield per arithmetic consume cause 17k shield and 3 fortress is a lot of drawback for just 1 arith, what if your card is expensive? You would not be able to break the shield ever? I suggest changing from per arithmetic consume to just consume arithmetic no matter the cost.", "timestamp": "2025-10-14T08:46:13.876000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-14T16:40:45.715000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1427578233431261295", "filename": "ScreenRecording_10-14-2025_15-37-27_1.mov", "content_type": "video/quicktime", "size": 3113937, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1427578233032937576/1427578233431261295/ScreenRecording_10-14-2025_15-37-27_1.mov?ex=69cc3295&is=69cae115&hm=edaa9b7bf2c754581feccb3abf6ec8e5e65512b9ea280317c50a7a28026a4d48&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1427578233032937576", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Ogier bugged?", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168939622727801", "1361168893200044183"]}
